reviewText: For this is haft true as to Adolf Hitler he for 1 thing did not kill himself in W W 2

Someone should check their history before writing a review. The Soviets found a body they 'claimed' was that of Hitler. However, after the fall of the Soviet Union, the remains were allowed to be viewed....and it was found that they/it were the remains of a woman. Now the last time I checked, Hitler was a man. Explain that.
With all the emphasis on "modern day FBI forensic science" the DVD virtually ignores that the Soviets found Hitler's body and confirmed it through dental records in 1945.
I was expecting it to be like the History Channel series. Disappointed.
